## Customizing histograms



::: {.cell output-location='column'}

```{.r .cell-code  code-line-numbers="|2|3-7"}
ggplot(loans, aes(x = loan_amount)) +
  geom_histogram(binwidth = 5000) +
  labs(
    x = "Loan amount ($)",
    y = "Frequency",
    title = "Amounts of Lending Club loans"
  )
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](3-3-1-visualize-summarize-numerical_files/figure-revealjs/unnamed-chunk-7-1.png){width=576}
:::
:::



## Fill with a categorical variable



::: {.cell output-location='column'}

```{.r .cell-code  code-line-numbers="|5,10"}
ggplot(
  loans, 
  aes(
    x = loan_amount, 
    fill = homeownership
    )
  ) +
  geom_histogram(
    binwidth = 5000,
    alpha = 0.5
  ) +
  labs(
    x = "Loan amount ($)", y = "Frequency",
    title = "Amounts of Lending Club loans",
    fill = "Homeownership"
  ) +
  theme(legend.position = "bottom")
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](3-3-1-visualize-summarize-numerical_files/figure-revealjs/unnamed-chunk-8-1.png){width=576}
:::
:::



## Facet with a categorical variable



::: {.cell output-location='column'}

```{.r .cell-code  code-line-numbers="|14"}
ggplot(
  loans, 
  aes(
    x = loan_amount, 
    fill = homeownership
    )
  ) +
  geom_histogram(binwidth = 5000) +
  labs(
    x = "Loan amount ($)", y = "Frequency",
    title = "Amounts of Lending Club loans",
    fill = "Homeownership"
  ) +
  facet_wrap(~ homeownership, nrow = 3) +
  theme(legend.position = "bottom")
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](3-3-1-visualize-summarize-numerical_files/figure-revealjs/unnamed-chunk-9-1.png){width=576}
:::
:::



